reviewText: I live in Burbank and thought I'd view it for fun. It's, well--what can I say? The title kind of tells it all. It's a comedy about girls with big fangs and big....well...

Pretty gory,bloody movie! Girls were sexy and story line was pretty good. It's a girls get revenge on guys movie by becoming predators themselves.movie ends pretty good.only thing I didn't like too much was how they got to be predators. They could've come up with something a little bit more beleiveable. Pretty good low budget horror movie though. James.
